{"title":"青年心中的雕像","authors":["林乐山"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":5,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"青年心中的雕像"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林乐山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张思德"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在中国西北的安塞烧炭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"很平凡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在长征路上踩着警句走过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"很平凡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被长了眼的子弹咬过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"很平凡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被一位伟人拉着手领进书本"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便升腾起火焰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟人那章遗篇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少人贴在心口上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"取暖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雷锋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当中国的最后一辆“解放”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驶下生产线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们倍加珍惜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一张与“解放”合影的照片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草绿色的背景前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"圆圆的娃娃脸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑出了一个时代"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反光镜那个亮呀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那才真叫一尘不染……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当中国的大路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“解放”牌逐渐被新的品牌取代"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们愈加怀念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一张珍贵照片里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一位年轻战士紧握的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的方向盘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"焦裕禄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煎熬一生风风雨雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把自己煎成一服中草药"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"专治一种"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫做贫穷的疾病"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一剂苦味的药"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"散发着荣誉的芳香"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已将面黄肌瘦的土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喝得大汗淋漓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也会分泌眼泪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真诚的情感最经得起熬煎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当成材的泡桐披上绿叶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们说青春便是春天"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}